CHANGELOG — make_szx.py
=======================

0.3.0 — 2026-03-11
  Updated GAME_START signature from DI+LD SP,$BFF8 (F3 31 F8 BF)
  to DI+LD SP,$BF00 (F3 31 00 BF) to match Fix 25b stack move.
  Updated Z80R chunk SP initial value from $BFF8 to $BF00.

0.2.0 — 2026-03-11
  No changes this session. Version bumped to match marco128.asm.

0.1.0 — Previous session
  Initial version. Reads bank*.bin, injects IM2 table into bank5,
  writes JP $BC00 at $BCBC in bank2, patches Z80 registers and SPCR
  for correct 128K snapshot state. Detects GAME_START via DI+LD SP
  signature search in bank2.bin.
